{"tid":1153133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國宣佈6月1日提高對美關稅","createTime":"2019-05-13T12:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T16:27:02.000Z","uid":164771,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c29914d2465e5d0715e3c6848b29a3f89eb51349","tid":1153133,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T12:21:55.000Z","msg":"對《國務院關稅稅則委員會關於對原產於美國約600億美元進口商品實施加徵關稅的公告》（稅委會公告〔2018〕8號）中部分商品，提高加徵關稅稅率，按照《國務院關稅稅則委員會關於對原產於美國的部分進口商品（第二批）加徵關稅的公告》（稅委會公告〔2018〕6號）公告的稅率實施。即：對附件1所列2493個稅目商品，實施加徵25%的關稅；對附件2所列1078個稅目商品，實施加徵20%的關稅；對附件3所列974個稅目商品，實施加徵10%的關稅。對附件4所列595個稅目商品，仍實施加徵5%的關稅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.wallstreetcn.com/articles/3527745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.wallstreetcn.com%2Farticles%2F3527745&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT5E%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=db347ef0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.wallstreetcn.com/articles/3527745</a>"},{"pid":"2f039e37ee2e8e451d0f985ccc0a50a9cb58ac79","tid":1153133,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef58f2386ee40c20b17195d3f8bbd604a68c327a","tid":1153133,"uid":249971,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T12:23:07.000Z","msg":"600億 vs 2000億"},{"pid":"4cbd96f5e22b5d50c373ca21f77535868ac86a83","tid":1153133,"uid":20609,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T12:25:05.000Z","msg":"侵侵快手上埋3000億"},{"pid":"9fe18eca0e4e990e9d68d559579e6f10ebf9972c","tid":1153133,"uid":7369,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T12:26:38.000Z","msg":"把劍就短咗d，但都算亮過啦！<br />\n<br />\n留名等睇侵侵反應"},{"pid":"eb34deab27409495c098736fc4a1101ccabcc65c","tid":1153133,"uid":125193,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T12:26:40.000Z","msg":"Trump 應該會好嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" c